# FastAPI Client Manager

REST API for client management.

## Stack
- Python
- FastAPI
- PostgreSQL
- SQLAlchemy

## Endpoints
- `GET /clients` — all clients
- `GET /clients/{id}` — client by id
- `POST /clients` — create a client
- `PUT /clients/{id}` — update a client
- `DELETE /clients/{id}` — delete a client

## Run
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn fast:app --reload

Create file `.env`:
```
DB_USER=...
DB_PASSWORD=...
DB_HOST=localhost
DB_PORT=5432
DB_NAME=...
DATABASE_URL=
SECRET_KEY=
```